data.title: The Bladerunner by Alan E Nourse 1975 Ballantine Books 1st Printing Paperback
data.meta_description:
This vintage paperback book titled "The Bladerunner" by Alan E. Nourse is a must-have for any science fiction enthusiast. Published by Ballantine Books in 1975, this first edition novel is a true gem for collectors. The book is set in the future and follows the story of a blade runner, a skilled assassin who is tasked with eliminating dangerous criminals.


The book is in great shape and has been well-preserved, making it an excellent addition to any vintage book collection. It features the author's signature and is an excellent example of his work. The intended audience for this book is adults, and it is sure to captivate anyone who enjoys science fiction.
